{"tid":1027432,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"睇睇下，我發現沙利先係問題所在","createTime":"2019-02-18T21:38:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T04:44:04.000Z","uid":44445,"like":79,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"8a2da436a09f095e3af2c34f4e0c30f2b55e4815","tid":1027432,"uid":44445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T21:38:00.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，場場個陣用人踢法都一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連盃仔都唔畀多啲機會後備球員<br />\n第五輪咋，龍門已經用緊Kepa<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔換人嘅問題一嚟係球員都踢到攰哂，二嚟係球隊冇咗兢爭嘅動力，反正踢到點柒，正選都係正選；反正點努力，後備永遠都係後備<br />\n咁搞法，更衣室遲早又出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再講，踢法千遍一律，對手盲嘅都識點應對啦<br />\n不論贏定輸緊，每場嘅換人都係一撚樣<br />\n姐係你落後緊，換人除咗係帶嚟新活力，亦係一個機會畀你用第二套戰術去攻<br />\n偏偏沙利換完人之後，用嘅又係同一套戰術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢嘅執著程度可以話係超越雲加<br />\n人地雲加都叫不敗奪冠，有理由畀佢執著咁踢<br />\n沙利憑咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連冠軍都未拎過（係拿玻里都係得第2）<br />\n好心你就聽下人講，諗下有冇plan B<br />\n唔係你就快啲執包袱走人啦"},{"pid":"2a6b262a1806430a838473b30769db6f0f6d0471","tid":1027432,"uid":18276,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T21:43:03.000Z","msg":"疤個華狗問題都俾你發現埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d2fa82899ba61f4de14643f41d22573b4a91f73","tid":1027432,"uid":218716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T21:43:33.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"37776be3d476f8e0170086a44103847a463521a6","tid":1027432,"uid":44445,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"2a6b262a1806430a838473b30769db6f0f6d0471","tid":1027432,"uid":18276,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T21:43:03.000Z","msg":"疤個華狗問題都俾你發現埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T21:48:44.000Z","msg":"咁都叫排緊榜首<br />\n我地第6咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkg